subject: Motorcycles, Motor Bikes and Motorscooters
lead_paragraph: The defending Dew Cup champion, Nate Adams, won the freestyle motocross event yesterday at the Dew Action Sports Tour’s Panasonic Open in Baltimore. Adams scored a 95.67 with multiple backflips. “Last year I won the first stop and ended up winning the whole tour,” he said. “I’m feeling pretty good.”.
